title: What is the type of singing that no one sings? - Quora

response.answer_text: Is this a 'self obscurating' question? It's too easy to say there is no singing that no one sings. Like a tree falling silently in the forest. But there are some extremely rare singing that virtually no one one sings except a very few individuals on this earth. Go ahead, look up on YouTube “Tibetan Throat Singing” . Very interesting, and learn something about Harmonics while your at it.
